This is release 1.1 of the scheme package.

---------------------- Compilation of the examples -----------------------

* First you must edit 'java-headers.scm' and set the variable
  'swing-path' to the correct value.

* If you have the 'make' command on your system, just type:

	    make

* Under Windows 95/NT type:

	    build

* If you do not have 'make' see 'Makefile' or 'build.bat'  for complete commands.


To run ScmApplet open 'SchemeApplet.html' with an HTML browser.

To run ScmInterpreter type:

	    java ScmInterpreter

To run ScmLoader type:

	    java ScmLoader file-name ...

where 'file-name' is the name of a scheme source file.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

For more details on this distribution read the HTML documentation in
the 'docs' directory.

